    aspect of our formation. With this regard, we allow and encourage our 
    students and all members of our school community to pray while 
    respecting their different beliefs. Prayers are scheduled as follows:
</p>
<br>
<h5>CATHOLICS: Sunday from 10h00 to 12h00</h5>
<br>
<h5>RAJEPRA: Sunday from 10h00 to 12h00</h5>
<br>
<h5>ADVENTISTS: Saturday from 10h00 to 12h00</h5>
<br>
<h5>ISLAM: Friday from 13:00 – 13:50</h5>

