<h4 class="about">CULTURE</h4>
<p>
    The school loves Rwandan culture and always strives 
    to preserving it. It is through school’s ITORERO called 
    IMBANGUKANABINGWI and CLUB OF “UMUCO N’UBUTWARI” that our 
    school continues to impart Rwandan cultural 
    values into her students and the rest of her whole community.
</p>